OL,3,CHow Spain's floods were driven by the
OL,4,CMediterranean's rising temperatures
OL,6,FWeather is driven by differences in
OL,7,Ftemperature. The bigger the difference
OL,8,Fthe more energy weather systems have
OL,9,Fand the higher the chance they become
OL,10,Fextreme.
OL,12,FWhat we're seeing in Spain is called
OL,13,FDepresion Aislada en Niveles Altos,
OL,14,Falso known as DANA (Spanish acronym
OL,15,Ffor high-altitude isolated depression).
