OL,3,CHow Spain's floods were driven by the
OL,4,CMediterranean's rising temperatures
OL,6,FIt's a phenomenon where cold air from
OL,7,Fthe North Atlantic meets warm humid
OL,8,Fair from the Mediterranean forcing the
OL,9,Fhot air to rise quickly and form huge
OL,10,Frain clouds that can then get stuck
OL,11,Fdumping enormous amounts of rain on
OL,12,Fthe land below.
OL,14,FThis often happens in the autumn but
OL,15,Fin recent years has become more
OL,16,Fextreme.
OL,18,FTo understand why we need to look at
OL,19,Fthe geography of the Mediterranean.
