OL,3,CHow Spain's floods were driven by the
OL,4,CMediterranean's rising temperatures
OL,6,FProfessor of climate change at the
OL,7,FUniversity of Reading, Richard Allan,
OL,8,Ftells ITV News how a drastic cutting
OL,9,Fof greenhouse gas emissions is needed
OL,10,Fto adapt to an increasingly 'dangerous
OL,11,Fworld'
OL,13,FBecause the entrance at the Strait of
OL,14,FGibraltar is so narrow, not much water
OL,15,Fmixes with the Atlantic, so the
OL,16,FMediterranean is more like a giant
OL,17,FLake than a sea.
