OL,3,CHow Spain's floods were driven by the
OL,4,CMediterranean's rising temperatures
OL,6,FOver the past 40 years climate change
OL,7,Fhas made Europe the world's fastest-
OL,8,Fwarming continent - the Mediterranean
OL,9,Fhas warmed twice as fast as the
OL,10,Fworld's oceans.
OL,12,FIn August we saw its hottest-ever
OL,13,Fsurface temperature recorded, 28.47C.
OL,15,FEven today surface temperatures are
OL,16,Fstill a degree above average. With no
OL,17,Fway to cool other than through
OL,18,Fevaporation - the air is more humid
OL,19,Fbecause it's holding more evaporated
OL,20,Fwater.
