OL,3,CHow Spain's floods were driven by the
OL,4,CMediterranean's rising temperatures
OL,6,FIn the words of one meteorologist, the
OL,7,Fresult is the Mediterranean is acting
OL,8,Flike a "petrol can" - the water vapour
OL,9,Ffeeding the devastating record-
OL,10,Fbreaking rain.
